                    },
                    "body": "Affects Version 1.9.6 and 1.9.7\r\nIn addition, maybe the priority level should be change to critical (loss of data).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=seb777",
                        "name": "seb777",
                        "displayName": "S\u00e9bastien Debrard",
